  "description": "<p><b>Overview:</b><br/>Pet collar, nylon dog collar, cat collar<br/>Comfortable, durable, unlimited<br/>1. Open the plastic buckle<br/>2. Use the daily buckle to adjust the size of the collar to fit the size of the pet's neck.<br/>3. Use the lanyard to buckle and flatten the shoulder strap.<br/>4. Close the plastic buckle<br/>Applicable object: General for cats and dogs<br/><br/><b>Product information:</b><br/>Name: Soft nylon pet collar<br/>Color: red, rose red, pink, orange, green, black, blue, sky blue, purple<br/>Main fabric material: nylon<br/>Accessories: plastic buckle, metal D buckle, Japanese buckle, belt buckle<br/>Lining: Neoprene<br/>XXS: 1.0x (14-20 cm)<br/>XS: 1.0 times (22-35 cm)<br/>S: 1.5 times (27-43 cm)<br/>M: 2.0x (33-50 cm)<br/>Length: 2.5 times (36-56 cm)<br/>Material: imitation nylon<br/><br/><b>Neck circumference measurement method:</b><br/>Use a soft ruler to draw a circle on the widest part of the dog\u2019s neck, and reserve 2-3cm around the dog\u2019s neck, as shown in the figure.<br/><br/><b>Notes:</b><br/>Due to manual measurement, the actual size may vary by 1-2cm, please note<br/><br/><b>Packing list:</b><br/>Collar*1</p><p>\n\n\n\n\n</p><table width=\"876\" height=\"114\">\n<colgroup><col width=\"190\">\n<col width=\"208\">\n<col width=\"163\">\n<col width=\"72\">\n<col width=\"243\">\n</colgroup><tbody><tr height=\"19\">\n<td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"190\">Size</td><td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"208\">width</td><td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"163\">Collar</td><td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"243\">Applicable&nbsp;types</td>\n</tr>\n<tr height=\"19\">\n<td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"190\">XS</td><td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"208\">1.0cm</td><td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"163\">22-35CM</td><td class=\"et3\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"243\">Chihuahua,&nbsp;fox&nbsp;terrier,&nbsp;cat</td>\n</tr>\n<tr height=\"19\">\n<td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"190\">S</td><td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"208\">1.5cm</td><td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"163\">27-43CM</td><td class=\"et3\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"243\">Yorkshire&nbsp;Terrier,&nbsp;Maltese</td>\n</tr>\n<tr height=\"19\">\n<td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"190\">M</td><td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"208\">2.0cm</td><td class=\"et3\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"163\">33-48CM</td><td class=\"et3\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"243\">Beagles\uff0cShepherd&nbsp;dog</td>\n</tr>\n<tr height=\"19\">\n<td class=\"et2\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"190\">L</td><td class=\"et3\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"208\">2.5cm</td><td class=\"et3\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"163\">36-56CM</td><td class=\"et3\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"243\">Labrador,&nbsp;Rottweiler,</td>\n</tr>\n<tr height=\"19\">\n<td class=\"et2\" height=\"19\" width=\"190\"></td><td class=\"et2\" height=\"19\" width=\"208\"></td><td class=\"et3\" height=\"19\" width=\"163\"></td><td class=\"et5\" x:str=\"\" height=\"19\" width=\"243\">Golden&nbsp;Retriever,&nbsp;Husky</td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody></table><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17190144/2406220642080329700.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17190144/2406220642090320500.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17190144/2406220642090321400.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17190144/2406220642090322000.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17190144/2406220642090322700.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/17190144/2406220642090324300.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"/><br/>",
